	* doc/ref.texh (Octet Molding/Mashing): Rename menu entry
	from "Selected Notes About Some Types" to "Builtin Converters".
	(Consulting Existing Type Converters):
	Move tables and associated blurbs from here...
	(Builtin Converters): ...to here, the node/section
	renamed from "Selected Notes About Some Types".

2014-12-14  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[doc] Fix bug: Use ‘@vindex’ for type converters.

	Regression introduced in Guile-PG 0.45 w/ switch to Texinfo 5.0.
	Using ‘@cindex @code{...}’ loses if makeinfo indexes the result
	of ‘@code{...}’, i.e., w/ quotes, instead of the ‘...’ only.

	* doc/guile-pg.texi (converter): ...here, in this macro.

