	* doc/guile-pg.texi (Top): Update menu entry.
	* doc/ref.texh (Octet Molding/Mashing): Rename node/chapter from
	"Types Conversion"; update intro to define "molding" and "mashing".
	(Column Definitions): Update @pxref.
	(Result Transforms): Update @xref.

