	[boot] Revamp libpq configury.

	* configure.ac (PG_CHECK_DIR): Delete AC_DEFUN.
	(libpq, libpq-includes, libpq-lib): Delete AC_ARG_WITH.
	(NOTE_ENVVAR): New AC_DEFUN.
