	on them in "checking PostgreSQL particulars" section.
	(AC_CHECK_HEADERS): Check for libpq-fe.h and
	libpq/libpq-fs.h; if not found, error out.
	(AC_CHECK_DECLS): #include <libpq-fe.h> unconditionally.
	(PQ_LDFLAGS): Move ‘-lpq’ suffixing from here...
	(SUBLDFLAGS): ...to here.

