2011-06-02  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[build] Prefer libpq headers in $(includedir)/postgresql, if available.

	* configure.ac (AC_CHECK_HEADERS_ONCE): New macro call
	for <postgresql/libpq-fe.h> and <postgresql/libpq/libpq-fs.h>;
	if found and not overriden by env vars ‘PQ_CPPFLAGS’ and
	‘PQ_LDFLAGS’, check for libpq.a as well, and set those vars.

